                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Merry</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-02-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 28, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Government of Nicaragua asserts duress from the naval forces at the capital of
                    Mosquito Territory, requesting strict neutrality. Fortytwo Americans have
                    surrendered to the naval forces occupying the capital of Mosquito Territory.
                    Government of Nicaragua promises lives, demanding trial by law. Illegal
                    expedition New Orleans leaving for Honduras, Nicaragua. Prevention is
                    requested.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Merry.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
